We artificially set start = 0 for each gap time interval by including `gtime` instead of `start, stop` in the `Surv()` object.



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
PWPgt <- coxph(Surv(gtime, event) ~ as.factor(rx) + number + size + strata(enum),
            ties = "breslow",
            cluster = id,
            data = bladder2)
summary(PWPgt)
```

